title: Teesside's Josh Daniel in X Factor final six boys
text:
Teesside singer Josh Daniel has made it through to the final six boys on The X Factor, mentored by radio DJ Nick Grimshaw. Josh will go to Judges Houses representing the North East. If he makes it through that stage, he will feature on the live shows on ITV.
nick grimshaw @grimmers Follow So there we go! My final 6 boys! Got some winners in there??
